        Register your<br>shop for<br><em>wholesale</em><br>tire prices
      </h1>
      <p class="wh-hero__sub">
        Are you an <strong>auto shop, mechanic, dealership, or fleet manager?</strong> Get exclusive trade pricing on all major tire brands. Apply in minutes, approved within 24 hours.
