<div class="wh-section wh-section--alt">
  <div class="wh-section__inner">
    <div class="wh-section__hd wh-section__hd--center">
      <span class="wh-eyebrow">Common questions</span>
      <h2 class="wh-h2">Frequently asked questions</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="wh-faq" style="max-width:760px;margin:0 auto">
      <div class="wh-faq-item">
        <button class="wh-faq-btn" aria-expanded="false">
          Is there a minimum order requirement?
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="wh-faq-body">No minimum order. You can order a single tire at wholesale pricing. Volume discounts apply as your monthly order volume increases — but there's no requirement to hit a minimum.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="wh-faq-item">
        <button class="wh-faq-btn" aria-expanded="false">
          How much can I save compared to retail?
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="wh-faq-body">Savings vary by brand, model, and your monthly volume. Higher-volume partners at Platinum and Elite tiers access the deepest discounts. Contact your account manager for a specific quote on the brands you buy most.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="wh-faq-item">
        <button class="wh-faq-btn" aria-expanded="false">
          How long does approval take?
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="wh-faq-body">Most applications are reviewed and approved within 24 hours during business days. You'll receive an email confirmation as soon as your account is activated. In many cases, same-day approval is possible.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="wh-faq-item">
        <button class="wh-faq-btn" aria-expanded="false">
          Do I need a business registration or GST number?
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="wh-faq-body">It's not strictly required, but providing your business registration or GST number helps speed up the approval process. We accept applications from all types of automotive businesses, including sole proprietors and mobile operators.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="wh-faq-item">
        <button class="wh-faq-btn" aria-expanded="false">
          Can I get wholesale pricing on installations too?
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="wh-faq-body">Yes — wholesale partners receive discounted installation rates for fleet work. We can schedule multiple vehicles at once around your operational hours. Contact your account manager to set up fleet terms.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="wh-faq-item">
        <button class="wh-faq-btn" aria-expanded="false">
          I already have a Prince Tires account. How do I upgrade to wholesale?
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="wh-faq-body">Sign in to your account first, then revisit this page — you'll see a direct option to apply for wholesale access linked to your existing account. Alternatively, visit <a href="/pages/wholesale-register" style="color:#DC2626">the application page</a> while logged in.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{%- comment -%} ── SAVINGS CALCULATOR ── {%- endcomment -%}
<div class="wh-section">
  <div class="wh-section__inner">
    <div class="wh-calc" id="WholesaleCalc">
      <div class="wh-calc__left">
        <span class="wh-calc__eyebrow">Savings calculator</span>
        <h2 class="wh-calc__title">How much could your shop save?</h2>
        <p class="wh-calc__sub">Drag the slider to estimate your monthly tire volume and see your annual savings at wholesale pricing.</p>

        <div class="wh-calc__label">
          Monthly tire volume
          <span id="CalcVolumeDisplay">20 tires/mo</span>
        </div>
        <input
          type="range"
          class="wh-calc__slider"
          id="CalcSlider"
          min="1"
          max="150"
          value="20"
          aria-label="Monthly tire volume"
        >
        <div class="wh-calc__ticks">
          <span class="wh-calc__tick">1</span>
          <span class="wh-calc__tick">30</span>
          <span class="wh-calc__tick">75</span>
          <span class="wh-calc__tick">100+</span>
        </div>

        <div class="wh-calc__avg-price">
          <div class="wh-calc__avg-label">Average tire retail price (customize)</div>
          <div class="wh-calc__avg-inputs">
            <span class="wh-calc__price-label">$</span>
            <input
              type="number"
              class="wh-calc__price-input"
              id="CalcRetailPrice"
              value="180"
              min="50"
              max="1000"
              step="10"
              aria-label="Average tire retail price"
            >
            <span class="wh-calc__price-label">per tire</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="wh-calc__right">
        <div class="wh-calc__tier-badge wh-calc__tier-badge--silver" id="CalcTierBadge">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="12" height="12"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87L18.18 21 12 17.77 5.82 21 7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          <span id="CalcTierName">Professional tier</span>
        </div>
        <span class="wh-calc__savings-num" id="CalcSavings">$0</span>
        <p class="wh-calc__savings-label">estimated annual savings vs. retail</p>

        <div class="wh-calc__breakdown">
          <div class="wh-calc__breakdown-row">
            <span>Monthly spend at retail</span>
            <span id="CalcRetailMonthly">$3,600</span>
